<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Support Request</title>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>Support Request</h1>
  <p>Dear Support Team,</p>

  <p>We have received a support request from a user. Below are the details:</p>

  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Name:</th>
      <td>{{ name }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Email:</th>
      <td>{{ email }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Subject:</th>
      <td>{{ subject }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th>Message:</th>
      <td>{{ message }}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>Please take appropriate action to address this support request promptly.</p>

  <p>Thank you for your attention and assistance.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>
    Nubis Logistics Team</p>
</body>

</html>